title: Spliced Business Formations Within Four Quarters: Total for All NAICS in Missouri
notes:
This series combines (splices) BFBF4QTOTALSAMO (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFBF4QTOTALSAMO) and BFPBF4QTOTALSAMO (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFPBF4QTOTALSAMO) to provide the entire time series for the actual and projected business formations within four quarters.

See the U.S. Census's FAQs (https://www.census.gov/econ/bfs/faqs.html) for more details.
